content:
Use Fundraising Updates for Advancement

Provide new and easy ways to acknowledge donors, enter new recurring donations, store the seasonal addresses of constituents, understand donor behavior to positively affect outreach, and report on and build lists of donors.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer editions where the Education Cloud license and Fundraising are enabled.

Who: Users with the Education Cloud Full Access permission set can access Fundraising.
title: Summer '24 Release Notes for Education Cloud
